Class User

java.lang.Object
model.User
public class User extends Object
Represents a user in the system with basic profile information, unique identifier, creation and activity timestamps, and a list of roles.
Version:
0.1
Author:
Artur Twardzik

  • Constructor Details

    • User

      public User(String name, String surname, String username)
      Constructs a new User with the specified name, surname, and username. Initializes the user with a unique ID, the current timestamp, and a default role.
      Parameters:
      name - The first name of the user.
      surname - The last name of the user.
      username - The username for the user.
